# Manage

#### Manage <a id="manage"></a>

This module is related to clients business managing, including users distribution,permission setting, logo setting and other information indication etc.

**Role**

Create new role and set the role functions permission and devices permission.

* _\*Function permission_ It shows the users of this role of certain operation accordingly.
* **Devicecs permission** It shows users of certain devices operated.

![Alt text](data:image/gif;base64,)

**User**

After creating new user, set the basic information and then the users role, then the user will have the role authority. If modification is needed, users authority can be re-modified in Users.

![Alt text](data:image/gif;base64,)

**Setting**

LOGO, users managing, complicated password, users locking settings can be equipped.  
Logo can be changed as below, after changing, platform logo can be replaced by self-determined Logo.

![Alt text](data:image/png;base64,)
